com.jbion.ces.actigraph

Class ActigraphCsvReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jbion.utils.csv.CsvReader
      • com.jbion.utils.csv.TimestampedCsvReader
        • com.jbion.ces.actigraph.ActigraphCsvReader

  • public class ActigraphCsvReader
extends TimestampedCsvReader
    A reader for the CSV file produced by ActiLife when exporting the actigraph's epochs. All the constants relative to the organization of the CSV file are hardcoded in this class.
    Author:
    Joffrey BION
